PcP Tools

By Marcel Borsten, Impart IT

Description:

PcP Tools is a script to support additional functionality in your Podcast Producer Workflows. It aims
to support functions that are not supported by the Mac OS X Snow Leopard build-in script 'pcastaction'.

Features:

At the moment PcP Tools supports uploading to Youtube and autosplit.

Example:

pcptools publish2youtube --basedir=<working directory> \
--input=<input filename> \
--dev_id=<your dev_id> \
--user=<your youtube loginname> \
--pass=<your youtube password> \
--keywords=<keywords> \
--category=<valid youtube category> \
--title=<title> \
--description=<description> \
--autosplit \
--outfile=</path to outfile>

--autosplit and --outfile are optional